  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494220/extras/d2408c83f08356e0ca43db98d804b810.avif?t=1749586429\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494220/extras_big/d2408c83f08356e0ca43db98d804b810.avif?t=1749586429 width=800 height=102 /></span>🐾 <strong>A Short & Whisker-Twitching Adventure!</strong> 🐾</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the paws of a curious cat in this choice-driven, storybook-style game!<br>Explore, interact, and make decisions that shape your journey, whether that means making friends, causing mischief, or discovering something unexpected.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What’s in the Box?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Be a Cat</strong> - Nap, explore, knock things over, and do what cats do best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Make Choices</strong> - Your decisions shape the story, leading to different outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Meet Quirky Characters</strong> - Befriend (or bother) a cast of charming animal NPCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a short and delightful game, perfect for a cozy playthrough in a single sitting. Where will your paws take you? 🐱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494220/extras/d2408c83f08356e0ca43db98d804b810.avif?t=1749586429\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494220/extras_big/d2408c83f08356e0ca43db98d804b810.avif?t=1749586429 width=800 height=102 /></span>🐾 <strong>A Short & Whisker-Twitching Adventure!</strong> 🐾</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the paws of a curious cat in this choice-driven, storybook-style game!<br>Explore, interact, and make decisions that shape your journey, whether that means making friends, causing mischief, or discovering something unexpected.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What’s in the Box?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Be a Cat</strong> - Nap, explore, knock things over, and do what cats do best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Make Choices</strong> - Your decisions shape the story, leading to different outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Meet Quirky Characters</strong> - Befriend (or bother) a cast of charming animal NPCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a short and delightful game, perfect for a cozy playthrough in a single sitting. Where will your paws take you? 🐱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
